text: Phira'aunale bhan'yoh, ki mero ajna begaira timiharule usamathi imana lyayau? Niscaya nai yahi timi sabaiko pramukha nayaka ho, jasale timila'i jadu sika'eko cha. Tasartha sighra nai timiharule thaha pa'ihalne chau. Ma sapatha linchu ki ma timra hata ra khuttaharu viparita disaharubata kata'idinechu ra timi sabaila'i phamsima jhundya'idinechu
